{"type": "article", "id": 58537, "title": "Moncler 为宠物狗推出羽绒服，迪士尼和小米推联合主题 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-11-21T04:37:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}, {"id": 1099, "name": "资生堂"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181121122316zBidrN2IstWGcLMT.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"XNHJ\"><b><a href=\"https://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/products/shiseido-names-naomi-osaka-brand-ambassador-1202909916/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">网球选手 Naomi Osaka 成为资生堂全球代言人，</a>她</b>也会为 BareMinerals 和防晒品牌 Anessa 代言。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122357QE9wvbSXFa5uP2zO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"ixHb\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BqNWeX7l6NG/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Moncler 与 Poldo Dog Couture 为宠物狗推出奢华羽绒外套，</b></a>还有背心和有帽外套。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122434oD1UFja04vh9IMTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122435R1WIx6s5EZgVpbXw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122435j3kyoe9Dx1WpT5aX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122436Ph0gDUWaJ1329vFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"UX7c\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4308507098201290?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>迪士尼联合小米手机推出了米奇专属手机皮肤主题，</b></a>依然是庆祝“米奇 90 周年”。“京沪蜀粤”四组主题加入了每个地域的传统特色，为了看起来更有“中国风”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122504SWgpMA56EcK9uTRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122506OXqkgM9avNZA2rjR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122507EvLi62twMoJA0eb9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122508uYhgvsIkNXqpAdo4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122509qG3mLewT6apJzIEu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122510mBXUeGyDw4uqKHER.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811211225106XZeJKadU8E1OHFN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122530l8ULuSPt4QRvzYHy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122530It0KbFSC7gdxMRVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"CQQr\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4308514903705771\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>优衣库 KAWS 和“芝麻街”第二波合作系列将于 11 月 22 日正式发售。</b></a>这一系列还是卫衣和 T 恤，线上旗舰店首发礼盒装玩偶在，然后才是门店和官网。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122602vNFZngXKWV2RuJmG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122654MTyIOYRHfzrQgF83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121122658Dhn4rfGj92osmU35.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"0tsO\">PEACEBIRD MEN 联合 GQ 实验室发布了“跨坎青年关怀计划”第 2 期，<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDA1ODAzMg==&amp;mid=2651110401&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=7a5d0cbbd7ba3ef06f92368ee656d687&amp;chksm=bdba8f5e8acd06489a91dfe9b871da1f0a8762d492608118e79f94050f87353a66a19ef82a62&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=11212GgFWaChWmUKr6EVG6pn&amp;key=424e54978849d95681a1bd736fe3f32d81a7d9f7a88c6624b833316c186bfc50e0d8f29b70b2af38def13c935a3fea1cf972714252fea4d395ca1c707978de84682e928e873e07d96bc4543781ee70c0&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=qF7ewd7YAM8bUQH%2Bg9MPZuJKoPZEzzjDqTMmdYcq3s9%2FITQKQ9opP24egeaA4r%2FY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>这次瞄准了入职第 5 年的年轻人。</b></a>面对“放假”、“应酬”、“剩女”、“请客”和“装嫩”他们选择“装”来掩饰内心的无奈。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o0796kg9ps9\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"KdI6\">多米诺披萨最近为新出的芝士汉堡口味披萨发布了一系列广告片<b> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/XXjA4V_0YcA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">“The Official food of WTF!”</a>，</b>短片以分屏的形式展现了明明吃起来是披萨但拥有汉堡口感和体验的场景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o0798dr38hh\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"o3Ln\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/11/21/accenture-and-wpp-play-nice-shell-brings-the-consultancy-crm-fold/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>埃森哲互动将成为壳牌 CRM 代理商之一。</b></a>之前的 CRM 代理商伟门（Wunderman）依然还是壳牌的领衔代理商，接下来伟门继续提供策略规划和创意指导。埃森哲互动会通过它的客户体验部门来支持具体数字项目的执行。</p><p line=\"MIgF\"><b><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/11/20/after-missing-out-top-job-wpp-ibm-s-david-kenny-named-nielsen-ceo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">尼尔森任命 David Kenny 为新 CEO</a>，</b>他之前是 IBM Waston 和云平台负责人。在苏铭天离开 WPP 之后，他曾被接洽这一职位，然而他未能进入最后一轮。</p><p line=\"AdQs\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/11/20/ms-putting-instagram-higher-its-media-plan-amid-marketing-reset\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>玛莎百货已经将媒体预算更多的投入到 Instagram 上，</b></a>尝试 Instagram 的购物和 IGTV (长视频)功能。这一举措是为了吸引更多的年轻人消费，并希望三分之一的销售额是通过线上交易实现。</p><p line=\"uZu9\"><b><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/design/amazon-taking-30-percent-ad-sales-fire-tv/315678/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">亚马逊要求电视网络和发行商在 Fire TV 上的广告销售量减少 30%,</a> </b>这一部分将归亚马逊自己支配并保留其中的收入。在新条款发布之前，他们是可以保留全部的广告销售收入的。</p><p line=\"uZu9\" class=\"\">题图来自 Hypebeast</p>"}